


05/03/2021 - Practice 2 - Math class

-Math Class
-it provides useful methods for us to use and do math calculations
-max(), min(), random(), abs(), sqrt(), round()
-java.lang package


Math.max(x, y);
-it takes 2 numbers
-it returns the max number

Math.min(x, y);
-it takes 2 numbers
-it returns min number

Math.abs(a);
-it takes 1 number
-it returns the positive value of given number

Math.sqrt(x);
-it takes a number and returns the root of it

Math.random();
-it returns a number between 0.0(included) and 1.0(excluded)

Math.round(x);
-it takes a number
-it returns closest int to given number






